	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新年的电视节目里，<delay20 />
大家都会穿着可爱的传统服饰，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起来又华丽，真好呀～！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近还分出复古派和现代派来，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也有各种各样的花纹，<delay8 />都很漂亮啊。<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也得好好学习一下！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～！<delay40 />为什么感觉，
