<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />给你们看看回旋抽球的厉害～！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />作为一个偶像，<delay20 /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
